Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: find my starbucks coffee
des: Your journey to find your perfect Starbucks® coffee starts here! Take this simple coffee finder quiz to match your personal tastes with your coffee tastes. See how questions such as, “Do you love trying new things?” and “What’s your favorite flavor?” can help guide you to the cup that’s right for you. Just say “Alexa, find my Starbucks® coffee” to discover your taste profile and receive a recommendation for the perfect cup for you to enjoy at home. You can also choose to receive more information on your recommended coffee and add it to your Amazon shopping cart.Try taking the quiz a few times and see how different answers can help you learn about the different tastes of Starbucks® coffee!
